<p>Bybit was co-founded by Ben Zhou in March 2018 with the goal to offer a professional platform where Crypto traders can find an ultra-fast matching engine, excellent customer service, and multilingual community support. Bybit provides access to trading Crypto and Crypto Futures for clients outside of <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="https://www.bybit.com/en/help-center/article/Service-Restricted-Countries">excluded jurisdictions</a> with low minimum deposits to set up an account. For more information about <a href='https://www.bybit.com/en/help-center/article/Bybit-Deposit-FAQ#b' rel='nofollow' target='_blank'>Crypto</a> and <a href='https://www.bybit.com/en/help-center/article/FAQ-Fiat-Deposit' rel='nofollow' target='_blank'>fiat deposits</a>, see the Bybit documentation. Bybit also provides Crypto staking, initial DEX offerings, and community airdrops.</p>

<p>To view the implementation of the Bybit brokerage integration, see the <a href='https://github.com/QuantConnect/Lean.Brokerages.Bybit' rel='nofollow' target="_blank">Lean.Brokerages.Bybit repository</a>.</p>